Docker:
=========

- Makes really easy to install and run software without worrying about the setup and dependencies.
- Docker Image (single file with all deps and config ) run in the Docker container(instance of image to run the image).
- Docker is a platform or ecosystem around creating and running containers.



Namespace:
   - Isolating resources per process or group of processes.
   - isolates like (processes, harddrive, network, hostnames etc)
Control groups:
   - Limit the amount of resouces used per process such as memory , cpu usage , network bandwidth



